Parking was OK at the hotel, but it's lack of proximity to Duval St. meant driving downtown and paying at least $10 per night to park there.	There is free parking though it is too far to walk to the beaches and Duval St. from the hotel.	This hotel does not offer a free shuttle like the other Marriott properties, although it's only about a $10 cab ride down to Duval St.	This hotel was not far from downtown and activities - about two km from Duval Street.	Only down side is it's located on a very busy/noisy highway ( the main highway in & out of Key West) & is about 2 miles from downtown Key West.